1
00:00:57,039 --> 00:00:58,840
Lu Qi is actually talented

2
00:00:59,119 --> 00:01:00,359
in photography.

3
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:04,159
No wonder Jiang Yue likes her.

4
00:01:09,799 --> 00:01:10,239
Lu Qi.

5
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,280
Professor Chu.

6
00:01:13,359 --> 00:01:13,719
Sit.

7
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:17,719
Put it here.

8
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:25,799
I've seen your work.

9
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:28,000
Do you also think it's evil?

10
00:01:33,519 --> 00:01:33,920
Lu Qi,

11
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,480
you're special.

12
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:37,480
Your work is special too.

13
00:01:40,159 --> 00:01:41,519
My work

14
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,120
is the scene

15
00:01:43,359 --> 00:01:44,400
I saw

16
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:46,200
that day

17
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,079
when you took me to a near-death experience.

18
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:48,959
I was thinking

19
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:51,519
I'd thank you properly after I won the award.

20
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,640
Who knew

21
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,400
I didn't even make it through the initial selection.

22
00:01:58,920 --> 00:01:59,599
This is quite normal.

23
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,200
They're just some ordinary folks,

24
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,640
yet they think they're the best in the industry.

25
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,639
Using their

26
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:10,719
limited knowledge

27
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:12,360
to set rigid rules.

28
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,280
You expect these people

29
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,400
to discover geniuses,

30
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:17,960
talents,

31
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,080
and even more so, the quirky talents.

32
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,599
I can introduce you to Professor Müller,

33
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,520
the master of surrealist photography.

34
00:02:27,199 --> 00:02:27,919
Professor Müller.

35
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:30,080
I know him.

36
00:02:31,039 --> 00:02:32,240
He will like you.

37
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,280
He can take you to the international stage

38
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,319
and show the world

39
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:38,319
your extraordinary talent.

40
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,439
Really? When?

41
00:02:44,759 --> 00:02:45,319
Jiang Yue.

42
00:02:45,759 --> 00:02:46,840
why are you here?

43
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:50,680
I told you

44
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:51,719
if you harass her again,

45
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:52,479
I'll kill you.

46
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:55,919
Mr. Chu, let's go.

47
00:03:07,439 --> 00:03:08,599
You asked him to follow me, right?

48
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,520
I didn't ask him to follow you.

49
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:17,639
He found you during his mission

50
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,479
and informed me.

51
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,120
And

52
00:03:21,599 --> 00:03:22,840
what if I asked him to follow you?

53
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,199
If he hadn't told me

54
00:03:24,479 --> 00:03:25,800
what was going to happen between you and Chu Mo,

55
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,000
why were you so close just now?

56
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,319
I told you long ago

57
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:29,280
to stay away from him.

58
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:30,360
He's not a good guy,

59
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,159
and he's very dangerous.

60
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:32,120
Did I ever tell you

61
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:32,960
I don't want to

62
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,120
wander aimlessly anymore?

63
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,719
Mr. Chu is willing to recognize me.

64
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:36,319
He helped me.

65
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,919
He will introduce me to the international photography master,

66
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:38,919
Mr. Müller.

67
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,319
I have no reason to refuse him.

68
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,919
Let go of me.

69
00:03:48,439 --> 00:03:49,159
I'll accompany you

70
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,199
on your way.

71
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,360
Jiang Yue, let go of me.

72
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:17,519
Hello.

73
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,839
Mr. Chu.

74
00:04:20,759 --> 00:04:21,600
I'm sorry.

75
00:04:22,319 --> 00:04:22,800
It's okay.

76
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:25,800
Lu Qi,

77
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,360
I really like the work "Tearing".

78
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,439
I can't bear to see it

79
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:32,519
in a dark corner.

80
00:04:34,079 --> 00:04:35,120
So I took the liberty

81
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,000
to send it to Müller.

82
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,800
What did he say?

83
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:41,040
In the 1980s,

84
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,279
Müller made a series of promotional videos

85
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:44,360
for a jewelry brand.

86
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:45,879
That series of promotional videos

87
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:46,839
changed people's views

88
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:47,839
on luxury at the time.

89
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,920
The moment he saw your photo,

90
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:52,279
his impression of Hongdu Photography

91
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:53,079
changed.

92
00:04:53,839 --> 00:04:54,439
He told me

93
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:56,240
he really liked it,

94
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,839
as if he saw his younger self.

95
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,199
Really?

96
00:05:01,519 --> 00:05:02,800
Would Professor Chu lie to you?

97
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,120
Lu Qi,

98
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:05,839
Mr. Müller wants to meet you.

99
00:05:07,079 --> 00:05:08,120
When do you have time?

100
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:10,439
I can take you abroad to meet him.

101
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:13,959
I...

102
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,040
Your brother must be worried about you.

103
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,720
You can tell him

104
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,519
that I can take you abroad.

105
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:31,639
Jiang Yue,

106
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,560
are you going to find Mr. Chu Mo?

107
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,360
[Jiang Yue,]

108
00:05:46,399 --> 00:05:47,680
[the moment I saw you,]

109
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,199
[I knew you were dark inside.]

110
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:52,079
[But I didn't expect]

111
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:53,959
[that it was not just dark,]

112
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,040
[but also soul-stirring,]

113
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,360
[and mind-blowing evil.]

114
00:06:00,199 --> 00:06:00,759
Senior Gao,

115
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:03,519
have you seen Jiang Yue?

116
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,519
I can't get through to him.

117
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,160
Master wouldn't ignore your calls

118
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:06,879
for no reason.

119
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:08,319
Has something happened between you?

120
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,279
What could possibly happen between us?

121
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:12,439
Miss Lu Qi,

122
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:13,800
if I may be so bold,

123
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,439
before you came into this family,

124
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:19,360
Master and Mr. Lu had no conflicts,

125
00:06:19,759 --> 00:06:21,399
and no one ever found their weakness

126
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:22,240
and humiliated them repeatedly.

127
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,079
What do you mean?

128
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:26,040
Young Master's intuition is rarely wrong.

129
00:06:26,839 --> 00:06:28,879
Since he suspects that Chu Mo is the Butterfly,

130
00:06:29,279 --> 00:06:30,079
Butterfly?

131
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:32,360
You don't know?

132
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:36,720
Butterfly,

133
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,079
the highest-valued assassin on the dark web.

134
00:06:39,759 --> 00:06:40,600
As long as he appears,

135
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:42,720
it means death and bloodshed.

136
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:45,040
At first, his target was Young Master.

137
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,199
But he found

138
00:06:46,639 --> 00:06:48,399
it's hard to find a breakthrough with the young master,

139
00:06:48,959 --> 00:06:50,000
so he frequently

140
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,199
appeared in your life.

141
00:06:52,279 --> 00:06:54,720
Because he knows the young master values you.

142
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:58,759
A person

143
00:06:59,040 --> 00:06:59,839
will not approach another person

144
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:00,680
without a reason.

145
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:04,560
Chumo is more suspicious.

146
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:09,319
At the 100th anniversary of Zhangyi College,

147
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:11,240
you didn't go to the lecture,

148
00:07:11,959 --> 00:07:13,240
But you came to our school.

149
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:16,480
We're just an ordinary high school.

150
00:07:18,279 --> 00:07:18,879
Because of you.

151
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:21,439
So what's your purpose of contacting Qi?

152
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,040
I like her, just like you.

153
00:07:26,399 --> 00:07:27,959
It seems like a joke,

154
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:29,480
but actually,

155
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,279
it's really because of me.

156
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,360
Miss Lu Qi,

157
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:33,920
I don't hope...

158
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:36,199
But as far as I can see,

159
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,560
you have become the blade

160
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,120
to hurt the young master and destroy 3Z.

161
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:50,720
Professor Chu,

162
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,000
are you free now?

163
00:07:54,759 --> 00:07:56,160
Okay, I'll see you later.

164
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:59,040
You're still in contact with him?

165
00:08:00,319 --> 00:08:01,360
I know what I'm doing.

166
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,600
I'll see you later, Senior Assistant Gao.

167
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:05,959
Thank you.

168
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,439
If we can lure Chu Mo out,

169
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,720
we can find Jiang Yue

170
00:08:12,439 --> 00:08:13,160
and stop him

171
00:08:13,519 --> 00:08:14,759
from making a big mistake.

172
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:16,879
Is this mine?

173
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:17,560
Yes.

174
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:18,439
Thank you.

175
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:25,240
Didn't your brother come with you?

176
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:27,839
I sent him a message.

177
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:28,560
He'll be here in a while.

178
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:49,440
Mr. Chu,

179
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:52,720
I'm happy that Mr. Müller likes me.

180
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,960
And I'm also happy that you're willing to help me.

181
00:08:55,519 --> 00:08:56,559
But after careful consideration,

182
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,240
I think it's too hasty.

183
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,279
I can't repay such a big favor.

184
00:09:01,159 --> 00:09:03,080
Thank you for helping me.

185
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,440
I'll always remember it.

186
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,759
Jiang Yue,

187
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,240
what did you give her

188
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:10,639
to make her give up on Müller?

189
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,320
Do you know what you're talking about?

190
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:13,960
Yes.

191
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:16,320
That's good.

192
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,200
You two have a nice chat.

193
00:09:19,759 --> 00:09:20,279
I'll be going.

194
00:09:20,879 --> 00:09:21,600
Thanks for the coffee.

195
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,080
Well,

196
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,200
Mr. Chu,

197
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:34,360
he didn't do anything to hurt me,

198
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:37,000
but I shouldn't have

199
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,120
ignored your feelings.

200
00:09:48,519 --> 00:09:49,799
My life is already like this.

201
00:09:50,519 --> 00:09:51,679
I don't want your dream to be shattered.

202
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,200
I'll do my best

203
00:09:55,639 --> 00:09:56,919
to help you become who you want to be.

204
00:10:05,279 --> 00:10:07,320
Sir, it's okay to have someone with physical strength.

205
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,720
I'm just afraid of emergencies.

206
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,799
You can't deliver without Jiang Yue, right?

207
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,919
How about I cover for you

208
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:17,879
and go with him?

209
00:10:20,679 --> 00:10:21,120
Sir,

210
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,799
it takes at least 40 minutes

211
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:23,759
to get to the port from here.

212
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,120
We need to make a decision.

213
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:27,600
Otherwise, 3Z's reputation will be affected.

214
00:11:16,159 --> 00:11:16,639
Listen,

215
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:21,360
I can

216
00:11:22,399 --> 00:11:24,039
let you display Lu Qi's work,

217
00:11:25,799 --> 00:11:26,679
and I can also

218
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,480
hand over the entire Cloud Court

219
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,559
to you to manage.

220
00:11:29,879 --> 00:11:30,759
Hurry up and deliver the goods.

221
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,080
If you're late, you'll get nothing.

222
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,039
Be good,

223
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:06,879
don't wander off.

224
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:07,960
Okay, mom.

225
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:08,919
I'm off.

226
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,000
Bye.

227
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:16,200
Master,

228
00:12:16,559 --> 00:12:17,559
the theme exhibition

229
00:12:17,559 --> 00:12:18,600
is all works from famous masters.

230
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,440
The product layout has been agreed.

231
00:12:20,679 --> 00:12:21,960
There's no good place to display

232
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,000
Miss Lu Qi's works.

233
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:25,279
You need Mr. Lu's permission to change it.

234
00:12:25,559 --> 00:12:26,279
Don't worry about

235
00:12:26,519 --> 00:12:27,039
Lu Qi's business.

236
00:12:27,279 --> 00:12:27,759
Okay.
